data.description: New Price! Buyer Concessions of 10K at closing! Welcome to 108 Scotsburg Street, located in the Hutto Square Community in growing Hutto Texas. A Coventry 2020 New Build 3 bed/2 bath with study & added interior and exterior features.  The exterior curb appeal is beautiful with upgraded landscaping, stone and stucco exterior, designer front door and sidewalks. As you walk in the large open floor plan, the center kitchen island with designer granite takes center stage along with high ceilings, recessed lighting, stainless steel appliances and gleaming luxury vinyl floors. Light and bright windows that look into the fenced private back yard. Sprinkler system in both front/back yard with full gutters are an added bonus. Large garage with bump out and storage. Driveway is level and easy for parking.  Bedrooms have plush carpet, ceiling fans and walk in closets. Master bedroom is expanded with a sitting area. Master Bathroom has modern tiled  walk in (double) shower and double vanity.  Located close to all major shopping, big box stores, HEB, churches, schools, Hutto hot spots, hospitals and more!  Easy access to 79 and tollways. Easy access to 79 and tollways. Hutto is growing with excellent schools, new local businesses and large corporate hubs! Do not miss out on the opportunity to buy the Follet Floor Plan in Hutto Square!
